<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- THE PROBLEM                                 -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-section convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="convo-speaker">
    <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
    The problem
  </div>
  <div class="convo-divider"></div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">AI amnesia is costing you</h2>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    Every AI conversation starts from zero. Your frameworks, refined language, hard-won decisions — gone when the chat window closes. Rebuilt from scratch every time you start a new session, with a new AI, or bring in a collaborator.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    This isn't a prompting problem. It's an infrastructure problem. The knowledge you produce with AI has nowhere to live. No persistence. No provenance. No compound growth.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    <strong>Multiplist is the infrastructure layer underneath your AI tools.</strong> It captures meaning, organizes it, and makes it available to every AI you work with — across sessions, across tools, across time.
  </p>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- CORE FEATURES                               -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-section convo-section--wide convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="convo-speaker">
    <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
    What it does
  </div>
  <div class="convo-divider"></div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">Four layers. One intelligence field.</h2>

  <div class="convo-cards convo-reveal">
    <div class="convo-card">
      <h3 class="convo-card__title">The Vault</h3>
      <p class="convo-card__text">A persistent, searchable knowledge store. Every insight, decision, framework, and golden passage extracted from your conversations — organized, citable, always growing. The vault is yours, forever.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-card">
      <h3 class="convo-card__title">Extraction Engine</h3>
      <p class="convo-card__text">Automatic meaning extraction from AI conversations, documents, and calls. Nine extraction categories (decisions, frameworks, golden passages, definitions, and more) turn raw content into structured knowledge in seconds.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-card">
      <h3 class="convo-card__title">MCP Connectivity</h3>
      <p class="convo-card__text">Connect Claude, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and other AI tools to your vault via Model Context Protocol. Every AI you use shares the same knowledge base. No more re-explaining your context from scratch.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-card">
      <h3 class="convo-card__title">Studios & Containers</h3>
      <p class="convo-card__text">Separate workspaces for every business lane. Client work doesn't bleed into internal strategy. Your AI always knows which context it's operating in — the same discipline as a well-organized office.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

