  </div>
  <div class="convo-divider"></div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">Your intelligence compounds. Automatically.</h2>

  <div class="convo-phases convo-reveal">
    <div class="convo-phase">
      <div class="convo-phase__number">1</div>
      <div class="convo-phase__content">
        <h3 class="convo-phase__title">Import</h3>
        <p class="convo-phase__desc">Paste a conversation, upload a document, or connect a source. Multiplist ingests whatever you've been thinking with.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-phase">
      <div class="convo-phase__number">2</div>
      <div class="convo-phase__content">
        <h3 class="convo-phase__title">Extract</h3>
        <p class="convo-phase__desc">The extraction engine parses the content and surfaces the meaning — decisions made, frameworks defined, passages worth keeping. Each seed carries its source provenance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-phase">
      <div class="convo-phase__number">3</div>
      <div class="convo-phase__content">
        <h3 class="convo-phase__title">Search</h3>
        <p class="convo-phase__desc">Query your vault across all sources. Find that framework you built three months ago. Surface the decision context your team forgot. Citation always included.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-phase">
      <div class="convo-phase__number">4</div>
      <div class="convo-phase__content">
        <h3 class="convo-phase__title">Connect</h3>
        <p class="convo-phase__desc">Route your vault to Claude, ChatGPT, or any MCP-compatible AI. Every session starts with full context. Intelligence compounds instead of evaporating.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

