<!-- USE CASES                                   -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-section convo-section--wide convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="convo-speaker">
    <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
    Who it's for
  </div>
  <div class="convo-divider"></div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">Built for people who think seriously with AI</h2>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    Multiplist is for founders, operators, researchers, coaches, and creators who do their best thinking inside AI conversations — and need that thinking to persist, compound, and remain retrievable.
  </p>

  <div class="convo-cards convo-reveal">
    <div class="convo-card">
      <h3 class="convo-card__title">Founders & Operators</h3>
      <p class="convo-card__text">Stop rebuilding context every session. Your strategic thinking, market frameworks, and decision history live in the vault — available to you and every AI you delegate to.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-card">
      <h3 class="convo-card__title">Consultants & Coaches</h3>
      <p class="convo-card__text">Your methodology is your business. Multiplist preserves it as structured, citable knowledge — extractable from client sessions, searchable across engagements, never lost to a hard drive crash or a forgotten chat.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-card">
      <h3 class="convo-card__title">Teams Using AI</h3>
      <p class="convo-card__text">Create a shared source of truth for AI. Separate containers per project. Everyone works with the same context. No more prompt drift, inconsistent outputs, or knowledge that lives in one person's head.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- FAQ                                         -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-section convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="convo-speaker">
    <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
    Common questions
  </div>
  <div class="convo-divider"></div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">Frequently asked</h2>

  <div class="convo-faq convo-reveal">
    <div class="convo-faq__item">
      <h3 class="convo-faq__q">What is Multiplist?</h3>
      <p class="convo-faq__a">Multiplist is a meaning operating system — a platform that extracts structured knowledge from your AI conversations and stores it in a persistent, searchable vault. It solves AI amnesia: the systematic loss of context and insight that happens between sessions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-faq__item">
      <h3 class="convo-faq__q">How is Multiplist different from a note-taking app?</h3>
      <p class="convo-faq__a">A note-taking app stores what you paste into it. Multiplist extracts meaning — it reads your AI conversations and surfaces the decisions made, frameworks developed, and passages worth keeping. The vault grows automatically as you work, not by manual curation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-faq__item">
      <h3 class="convo-faq__q">What AI tools does Multiplist connect to?</h3>
      <p class="convo-faq__a">Multiplist connects to Claude, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and any AI that supports Model Context Protocol (MCP). Once connected, those AIs can query your vault directly — your knowledge becomes their starting context, not something you re-explain every session.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-faq__item">
      <h3 class="convo-faq__q">Is Multiplist part of the consulting service?</h3>
      <p class="convo-faq__a">Multiplist is the platform; Multiplist Studios is the consulting practice built on top of it. Consulting clients get their own Multiplist environment as part of the engagement. The product is also available independently at multiplist.ai.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-faq__item">
      <h3 class="convo-faq__q">What are MCP and the Model Context Protocol?</h3>
      <p class="convo-faq__a">MCP (Model Context Protocol) is an open standard that lets AI tools connect to external data sources and services. Multiplist uses MCP to share your vault with Claude, ChatGPT, and other compatible AIs — so every session starts with full context instead of a blank slate.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="convo-faq__item">
      <h3 class="convo-faq__q">Where do I sign up for Multiplist?</h3>
      <p class="convo-faq__a">Multiplist is available at <a href="https://multiplist.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">multiplist.ai</a>. If you're a consulting client, your environment will be set up as part of the onboarding process. If you're exploring independently, the free tier lets you start building your vault immediately.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

